 Essex, England":"英國艾可莎佛朗 瓦爾登","lifeSummary":"當Sir William Baker Lees於1524年出生在英國諾廷加姆爾武德波洛時，他的父親William Lees Sr24歲，母親Susanna Maelcot24歲。他於1541年與Mary Thornleigh結婚。他們至少是2個兒子和2個女兒的父母。他於1524年住在英國瓦維其可爾且於1545年住在英國艾可莎佛朗 瓦爾登。他去世於1545年在英國諾廷加姆爾武德波洛享年21歲。"},"zh-hans":{"1524–1545":"1524年–1545年","1525–1600":"1525年–1600年","1542–Female":"1542年–殁","1543–Male":"1543年–殁","1544–Male":"1544年–殁","1545–1600":"1545年–1600年","1500–Male":"1500年–殁","1500–Female":"1500年–殁","1525":"1525年","1524":"1524年","1545":"1545年","1600":"1600年","April 1542":"1542年4月","1544":"1544年","1500":"1500年","1543":"1543年","1542":"1542年","1541":"1541年","Woodborough, Nottinghamshire, England":"英国諾廷加姆爾武德波洛","Tanworth in Arden, Warwickshire, England":"英国瓦維其可爾坦沃斯 在 阿爾登","Warwickshire,England":"英国英格兰瓦維其可爾","Warwickshire, England":"英国瓦維其可爾","Warwickshire , England":"英国英格兰瓦維其可爾","Saffron Walden, Essex, England":"英国艾可莎佛朗 瓦爾登","lifeSummary":"当Sir William Baker Lees于1524年出生在英国諾廷加姆爾武德波洛时，他的父亲William Lees Sr24岁，母亲Susanna Maelcot24岁。他于1541年与Mary Thornleigh结婚。他们至少是2个儿子和2个女儿的父母。他于1524年住在英国瓦維其可爾且于1545年住在英国艾可莎佛朗 瓦爾登。他去世于1545年在英国諾廷加姆爾武德波洛享年21岁。"},"hr":{"1524–1545":"1524.–1545.","1525–1600":"1525–1600","1542–Female":"1542–preminula","1543–Male":"1543.–preminuo","1544–Male":"1544.–preminuo","1545–1600":"1545.–1600","1500–Male":"1500–preminuo","1500–Female":"1500–preminula","1525":"1525","1524":"1524.","1545":"1545.","1600":"1600","April 1542":"travanj 1542.","1544":"1544.","1500":"1500","1543":"1543.","1542":"1542","1541":"1541.","Woodborough, Nottinghamshire, England":"Woodborough, Nottinghamshire, England","Tanworth in Arden, Warwickshire, England":"Tanworth in Arden, Warwickshire, England","Warwickshire,England":"Warwickshire, Engleska, United Kingdom","Warwickshire, England":"Warwickshire, England","Warwickshire , England":"Warwickshire, Engleska, United Kingdom","Saffron Walden, Essex, England":"Saffron Walden, Essex, England"},"cs":{"1524–1545":"1524–1545","1525–1600":"1525–1600","1542–Female":"1542–Zesnulá","1543–Male":"1543–Zesnul